@startuml 14-activity-customs-clearance
title Activity Diagram — Customs Clearance Workflow

|Shipping Agent / System|
start
:Submit customs declaration;

|Customs Agent|
:Validate documents;
:Calculate risk score (ML);

if (Risk score > threshold?) then (high)
  |Customs Officer|
  :Manual review required;
  :Inspect supporting documents;

  if (Documents valid?) then (yes)
    :Approve with conditions;
  else (no)
    :Hold declaration;
    :Request additional docs;
    stop
  endif

else (low)
  :Auto-clearance eligible;
endif

|Customs Officer|
:Final clearance decision;

if (Approved?) then (yes)
  :Update status = CLEARED;
  :Publish customs.clearance event;
  :Notify billing agent;
else (no)
  :Update status = HELD;
  :Escalate to supervisor;
endif

|Billing Agent|
:Calculate port charges;
:Generate invoice;

stop

@enduml
